40	{"name": "AnotherWidget", "grep": "unique string", "description": "what it renders", "shared": true}
41	```
42	
43	## Extraction Criteria
44	
45	Extract a region when:
46	- It's a self-contained visual block (card, list item, section header)
47	- It has 15+ lines of widget code
48	- It could be reused across screens (`shared: true`)
49	- It has its own data/state concerns
50	
51	Do NOT extract:
52	- Simple `Text`, `Icon`, or `SizedBox` widgets
53	- Layout wrappers (`Padding`, `Center`)
54	- Anything under 10 lines
55	
56	## Success Criteria
57	
58	- `.stitch/designs/cycle-tracking/widgets.jsonl` exists with valid JSONL
59	- Each entry has: name, grep, description, shared
60	- Widget names use PascalCase
